; Regression test: Crypto FIFO with multiple lots and multi-posting sales
;
; Real-world scenario: Cryptocurrency trading with opening balances from
; different sources, purchases, and sales that include fees as separate
; postings. This tests the combination of:
; 1. Multiple lots with different cost bases
; 2. FIFO lot selection with empty {} cost specs
; 3. Multi-posting transactions crossing lot boundaries
;
; This pattern is common in crypto accounting where exchanges charge
; fees in the traded asset rather than in USD.

option "operating_currency" "USD"

2020-01-01 open Assets:Crypto:Kraken  ADA,USD  "FIFO"
2020-01-01 open Equity:Opening-Balances
2020-01-01 open Income:Crypto:Trading
2020-01-01 open Expenses:Crypto:Fees

; === Opening balances from different sources ===

; Lot 1: Legacy holdings (oldest - should be sold first via FIFO)
2021-01-01 * "Opening balance from cold wallet"
  Assets:Crypto:Kraken   350000 ADA {0.50 USD, 2021-01-01}
  Equity:Opening-Balances

; Lot 2: Recent transfer (note: included later in file but earlier date)
; This tests that date sorting works correctly regardless of include order
2022-05-19 * "Opening balance from another exchange"
  Assets:Crypto:Kraken   605489.04 ADA {0.5169 USD, 2022-05-19}
  Equity:Opening-Balances

; Lot 3: Purchases
2022-05-20 * "Buy ADA"
  Assets:Crypto:Kraken   100000 ADA {0.517 USD, 2022-05-20}
  Assets:Crypto:Kraken   -51700 USD

; === Sales with fees (multi-posting) ===

; This sale + fee together should:
; 1. Take from lot 1 first (FIFO) - all at $0.50
; 2. Fee posting continues from the same lot state
; Cost basis: 19090.32 ADA * $0.50 = $9545.16
2022-05-22 * "Kraken" "Trade - SALE" #kraken
  Assets:Crypto:Kraken    -19000 ADA {}           ; Main sale
  Assets:Crypto:Kraken       -90.32 ADA {}        ; Fee in ADA (multi-posting!)
  Assets:Crypto:Kraken   9545.16 USD              ; Proceeds = cost basis
  Income:Crypto:Trading

; Another sale exhausting lot 1 and dipping into lot 2
; Remaining in lot 1: 350000 - 19090.32 = 330909.68 ADA at $0.50
; Cost basis: 330909.68 * $0.50 = $165454.84
2022-05-23 * "Kraken" "Trade - SALE 2" #kraken
  Assets:Crypto:Kraken     -330909.68 ADA {}      ; Exhausts lot 1
  Assets:Crypto:Kraken    165454.84 USD           ; Proceeds = cost basis
  Income:Crypto:Trading

; Final balance check
; Lot 1: 350000 - 19090.32 - 330909.68 = 0 (exhausted)
; Lot 2: 605489.04 ADA remaining
; Lot 3: 100000 ADA remaining
2022-05-24 balance Assets:Crypto:Kraken  705489.04 ADA
